thread.title: What do you think of Syracuse basketball's new road jerseys?
thread.title_full: What do you think of Syracuse basketball's new road jerseys?

author: Chris Carlson | ccarlson@syracuse.com
title: What do you think of Syracuse basketball's new road jerseys?
text:
The Syracuse basketball team tweeted pictures of its new road jerseys Friday, a few hours before the team's scheduled media day. 
Here's our first look. â€” Syracuse Basketball (@Cuse_MBB) October 16, 2015 
The Orange jerseys look to have a new font, with both the numerals and the "Syracuse" done in white. Last year, the numerals were done in white and platinum at various points in the year. 
The font looks slightly different and the numbers have a blue trim around them, making them pop out a little more. 
The back includes a watermark with the that includes the year the school was established, 1870, on what looks to be a train. 
So, since we all enjoy playing fashion critic, what do you think?
